<section xml:id="sec-7-1-Solving_2x2_Systems" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Solving <m>2\times2</m> Systems of Linear Equations</title>
    <p><em>Solving <m>2\times2</m> Systems of Linear Equations</em> demonstrates the substitution 
        method and the elimination method for solving a system of two linear equations in two variables. 
        The connection to linear algebra, vector spaces and matrices is not done in this lesson.</p>
        
